                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-79-off450 t18000528-79-cd451"></join>, a black silk cloak, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000528-79-victim827" type="victimName">
                     Moses 
                     Moses
                  <interp inst="t18000528-79-victim827" type="surname" value="Moses"></interp>
